      <a href="https://app.quipthread.com">app.quipthread.com</a> (the "Service").
    </p>
    <p>
      By creating an account or using the Service, you agree to be bound by these Terms. If you
      do not agree, do not use the Service.
    </p>

    <h2>1. Service Description</h2>
    <p>
      Quipthread is a comment platform that lets website owners embed a hosted comment section on
      their pages. It is available as a cloud-hosted service (governed by these Terms) and as
      open-source software you can self-host under the{' '}
      <a href="https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
