      </a>.
      These Terms apply only to the cloud-hosted service.
    </p>

    <h2>2. Accounts</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>You must provide accurate and complete information when creating an account.</li>
      <li>You are responsible for maintaining the security of your account credentials.</li>
      <li>You must be at least 13 years old to use the Service.</li>
      <li>One person or legal entity may not maintain more than one account.</li>
      <li>
        You must notify us immediately at{' '}
        <a href="mailto:legal@quipthread.com">legal@quipthread.com</a> if you suspect
        unauthorized access to your account.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Acceptable Use</h2>
    <p>You agree not to use the Service to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Post spam, unsolicited advertising, or bulk automated content.</li>
      <li>Harass, threaten, or abuse other users.</li>
      <li>Upload or transmit illegal content, including content that infringes third-party intellectual property rights.</li>
      <li>Scrape, crawl, or systematically extract data from the Service without our written permission.</li>
      <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to any part of the Service or its infrastructure.</li>
      <li>Impersonate any person or entity.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Content</h2>
