    </p>

    <h2>5. Billing and Subscriptions</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        Paid plans are billed in advance on a monthly or annual basis. All payments are processed
        by Stripe.
      </li>
      <li>
        Subscriptions automatically renew at the end of each billing period unless cancelled
        before the renewal date.
      </li>
      <li>
        Cancellation takes effect at the end of the current paid period. You will retain access
