      </li>
      <li>
        Prices may change with 30 days' notice. Continued use after a price change constitutes
        acceptance of the new price.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>6. Free Trial</h2>
    <p>
      New accounts are eligible for a 14-day free trial on any paid plan. No credit card is
      required to start a trial. The trial is available once per account. If you add a payment
      method before the trial ends, your paid subscription begins automatically at the end of the
      trial period. If no payment method is on file when the trial ends, your account reverts to
      the free Hobby plan.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Termination</h2>
    <p>
      You may cancel your account at any time from the billing settings in your dashboard or by
      contacting us. We may suspend or terminate your account if you violate these Terms,
      without prior notice.
    </p>
    <p>
      Before terminating your account, you may export your data (comments and users) in JSON or
      CSV format from the dashboard.
    </p>

    <h2>8. Indemnification</h2>
